This project uses TypeScript in strict mode.

## Key Rules

- All code, comments, and documentation must be in English
- No `any` types — use `unknown` and narrow
- Validate all external inputs with Zod schemas
- Use shadcn/ui components for UI — don't create custom primitives
- Server Components by default — add "use client" only when needed
- Follow the project structure defined in AGENTS.md

## Testing

- Unit/integration: Vitest with MSW for API mocking
- E2E: Playwright
- Test files go in `__tests__/` directories next to the code they test
- Mock all external APIs (OpenAI, NewsAPI, etc.)

## Database

- Use Drizzle ORM — no raw SQL
- Schema changes: `npm run db:generate` then `npm run db:migrate`
- Use `cuid2` for IDs

## Commit Messages

Use conventional commits:
- `feat:` new features
- `fix:` bug fixes
- `chore:` maintenance
- `docs:` documentation
- `test:` tests